\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs30 Two months later, four days before the New Year, she had an accident. There was an elevator in the restaurant, they'd bring food up in an elevator. My wife got on the elevator, in the third floor the elevator cable broke and my wife fell and broke her spine.
\f1\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl400\partightenfactor0

