\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs30 00:21:08.460 --> 00:21:43.070
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs30 She to have surgery- $5,500 worth. They had to put 12 screws in her back. It was free from the Diaspora Ministry and the Healthcare Ministry provided for it because I am Syrian Armenian.
\f1\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl400\partightenfactor0

\f0\fs30 \cf2 53
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs30 00:21:43.090 --> 00:22:04.390
\f1\fs24 \

