\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs30 00:25:01.560 --> 00:25:32.040
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs30 There's a strange thing here with the local restaurants. They want a specialist and then ask your age when you apply. You're 50, they say you're too old for the job. You say, do you need a specialist or a young person? So, because of that, I didn't work for a year and a half.
\f1\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl400\partightenfactor0

\f0\fs30 \cf2 61
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs30 00:25:32.060 --> 00:26:20.460
\f1\fs24 \

