\pard\pardeftab720\sl400\partightenfactor0

\f0\fs30 \cf2 67
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs30 00:28:20.990 --> 00:29:07.380
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs30 Of course I wanted to help my brothers and mother, but I was myself in need of help here, in Armenia. I was unemployed in Armenia for a year. In this city, if you do not work one day, you are four months behind. This is not Aleppo. In Aleppo, if I did not work for one year, for example, it \'a0was ok, but here just one day of no work sets you back a year. Even your brother will not give you 100 drams in Armenia.
\f1\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl400\partightenfactor0

